headline: NFL Names NetApp the Official Intelligent Data Infrastructure Partner
summary: NEW YORK & SAN JOSE, Calif., April 15, 2025--The National Football League today named NetApp® (NASDAQ: NTAP) the Official Intelligent Data Infrastructure partner. NetApp will work with the league to develop cutting-edge, silo-free storage technology, allowing the NFL to manage the data to drive innovation.
